; https://github.com/tldr-pages/tldr/blob/master/pages/common/fresh.md

% fresh, common

# Open a file
fresh <path_to_file>

# Search for a pattern
<Ctrl f><search_pattern><Enter>

# Replace a pattern
<Ctrl r><search_pattern><Enter><replacement><Enter>

# Show File Explorer
<Ctrl e>

# Save file
<Ctrl s>

# Quit
<Ctrl q>
